#### draw a grid centered at the origin


<%= vroom_example_image "rendering", "grid", "draw-a-grid-centered-at-the-origin.png" %>


~~~ python
def display():
   lighting(False)
   size=20
   draw(grid, size, size, 10, 10).at([-size/2, -size/2, 0])
~~~

